#Question 5:
#Scenario:A data analytics tool needs to identify the highest value.
#Task:Write a program to find the largest among three numbers
a = int(input("Enter first number: "))
b = int(input("Enter second number: "))
c = int(input("Enter third number: "))

if a >= b and a >= c:
    print("Largest =", a)
elif b >= a and b >= c:
    print("Largest =", b)
else:
    print("Largest =", c)
